Name: The Monster PIMP
About the game: [Story] He wasn't very popular with the ladies... But he had a special power... He can see monsters that others can't! With supernatural events happening around town, he decides to use his abilities to find the monsters in hiding...! [Game system] Taking out the Evil Spirits Take out the 60+ Evil Spirits lurking around the world! Fight them using an orthodox turn-based fighting system. Monsters - Nekomata - Ittan-momen - Water Imp and many more! Try to find them all! Use special items at certain fights to unlock hidden events...!
